    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several large dents, significant paint peeling, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent oil leak, and the transmission shifts roughly; additionally, the air conditioning is non-functional and the tires need immediate replacement. The interior has multiple tears in the upholstery and a lingering musty odor, making this an ideal project car for someone with mechanical skills or a source for parts.",
