    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely pristine and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new but without that heavy new-car price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 43500.0,
