    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example is mechanically flawless, with a recently reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings to ensure long-term reliability. The naturally aspirated powerplant delivers linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. Suspension kinematics are sharpened by Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, providing exceptional turn-in and damping control. Meticulously maintained with no fluid seepage or diagnostic faults, this is a turn-key performance icon for the purist.",
